  "body": "### Version Information\r\n\r\nvyper.online\r\n\r\n### What's your issue about?\r\n\r\nThis line should cause a compiler error:\r\n\r\n`    self.a = blockhash(-20)`\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed?\r\n\r\nBlock numbers should be uint256. \r\n\r\nAlso, note that the `BLOCKHASH` opcode puts a 0 on the stack if the looked for block number is greater than or equal to the current block number or more than 256 blocks behind the current block.\r\n\r\nThis is a dangerous hole. I'm not sure the best way to plug it. \r\n\r\n",
